## Phase Summaries

**Phases 1-8** established the core game: coin economy, overgrowth difficulty, airplane flyovers, near-miss/objectives/jackpot juice, production hardening (81 tests, ESLint, Prettier), branding, micro-polish (VFX, celebrations, milestones), player experience (daily modifiers, vehicle unlocks, sound enrichment), and store readiness (v1.0.0).

**Phase 9 — Play-test Polish:** Specials overhaul (removed BLACKOUT/COOLDOWN/LURE, added BLUR/OIL_SLICK/REVERSE/MYSTERY). Toast system rework, game-over simplification, pause timer freeze, overlay transparency, ice physics tuning, viewport scaling, global settings.

**Phase 10 — Audio & Visuals:** Master gain increase, propeller biplane redesign with continuous drone audio, adaptive sprite contrast (dark outlines on bright pages, light glow on dark), extension popup.

**Phase 11 — Scoring & Naming:** All scores multiples of 10, near-miss visual-only, plain special names, airplane drop toast removed, police chase shortened.

**Phase 12 — HUD & Compatibility:** Merged info block, daily modifier label, Shift+Space hotkey, popup start button, scrollbar-gutter fix, unsupported page detection.

**Phase 13 — Audit & Branding:** Config consistency verified, dead code removed, all 10 systems confirmed distinct, branding SVGs with coupe sprite silhouette.

**Phase 14 — UX Truth Pass:** HUD controls fix (WASD/ARROWS, M key prefix, fixed columns), center-biased spawn, form control scanning (slow zones + overgrowth anchors), overgrowth ladder rewrite (grass → bush → tree), special pickup shape grouping (helpful=rounded square, harmful=diamond, mystery=circle).

**Phase 15 — Style & Docs:** Popup unified with HUD visual language, pixel-art SVG wordmark in branding, README shortened and corrected, store listing refreshed.

**Phase 16 — Encounter Discovery:** Helicopter design memo (chase-count trigger, airborne movement, rotor audio). Train/rail memo (obstacle post-processing, ~15-25% page coverage). See `docs/discovery-helicopter-train.md`.

**Phase 17 — Police Helicopter:** `PoliceChaseState.variant` ('car' | 'helicopter'). Helicopter spawns from chase #3+ via `POLICE.HELICOPTER_CHASE_THRESHOLD`. Airborne movement (ignores obstacles/ice), helicopter sprite with spinning rotor and searchlight, rotor chop audio replacing siren, amber "CHOPPER" edge warning, "CHOPPER - ESCAPE!" GOAL panel text. Ghost still dismisses. 6 new tests (87 total).

**Phase 18 — Train Encounter:** Rail detection from `<hr>` elements, CSS borders on wide containers, thin separator divs, and long thin obstacles/slowZones (aspect ratio >12:1, >60% viewport span). `TrainState` lifecycle (idle → warning → crossing → cooldown). Caltrain-style multi-car sprite with horizontal/vertical support. Train horn + crossing rumble audio. Yellow "TRAIN" edge warning. "HIT BY TRAIN" game over. Ghost immunity. Encounter stagger with police/plane. TRAIN config section (9 constants). 20 new tests (107 total).

**Phase 19 — Branding Pixel-Art Backgrounds:** Replaced smooth linear gradients in all three branding SVGs (icon, store cover, store tile) with pixel-art horizontal stepped color bands (dark navy → teal). Removed bezier sweep decorations and reduced decorative noise. PNGs regenerated via `rsvg-convert`.

## Phase Closeout Protocol

Every phase ends with a mandatory closeout pass before marking `done`:

1. **Refactor & simplify** — dead code, duplication, naming
2. **Productionize** — no debug artifacts, no `console.log`, no `__domRacerDebug`
3. **Tests** — updated, new coverage, `npm run test` green
4. **Lint & format** — `npm run lint:fix && npm run format`, zero warnings
5. **Build** — `npm run build` succeeds cleanly
6. **Docs** — update SOUL.md, README.md, next-session.mdc, phases.mdc
7. **Commit** — single clean commit summarizing deliverables

